title: WearCam (Unreleased)
summary: A simple Photo/Video/Gallery App for your Android Wear Smartwatch
description: Stream your Camera from your Smartphone easily to your Android Wear Smartwatch. You can take pictures/videos or preview taken pictures in the gallery through simple Touch/Swipe Gestures.Requirements: Android 5.0 (Smartphone) , Android 5.0 (Watch)
descriptionHTML:
Stream your Camera from your Smartphone easily to your Android Wear Smartwatch. You can take pictures/videos or preview taken pictures in the gallery through simple Touch/Swipe Gestures.

Requirements: Android 5.0 (Smartphone) , Android 5.0 (Watch)
